1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Wuz Good, Julia Price, DeStorm, and Taryn Southern are going to get a little wrecked playing Suck and Blow, Coconut Smoochie, Pickle Pecker, and Bend Over. There can only be one winner.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Steve Greene, Avital Ash, Peter Gilroy, and Danielle Renee get to know each other a little better playing Fast Candy, Never Have I Ever, Kiss or Slap, and Chubby Bunny.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Shanna Malcom, Justin James Hughes, Olga Kay, and Drew Monson compete in the Cottonball Challenge, Fuzzy Duck, Blindfolded Banana, and Clothespinned.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Lauren Francesca, Max No Sleeves, Dan Nampaikid, and Ceciley dare to play Weenie in a Bottle, Face the Cookie, Nikki Says, and Take the Plunge.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Nicola Foti, Lynette Cene, Courtney Sailors, and DavidAlvareeezy Hit the Orange, Pass the Cuke, Gummy Hunt, and Blind Draw.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: Josh Evans, Rebecca Zamolo, Liza Koshy, and PTrique get hilarious playing Cherry Poppin, Whats in the Bag, Truth or Dare, and Makeup Challenge.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Comedians Ricky Shucks, Syd Wilder, Michelle Glavan, and Alphacat face off in Spin the Lipstick, Would You Rather, Candy Game, and Whipped Bubblegum.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: Meghan Tonjes, Andrew Delman, Lee Newton, and Elliott Morgan battle it out in the games Most Likely, Whats in My Mouth, Straight Face, and Red Apple.

imdb.plot outline: YouTube star Nikki Limo hosts game night in her parents' living room - playing games from growing up like "Never Have I Ever" and "Spin the Bottle." The series is a collaboration between Maker Studios and Matador Content, producers of the hit Spike TV series Lip Sync Battle.
